title: BRIEF-WSFS Reaches Settlement With Universitas Education

organizations.name: brief-wsfs financial reaches settlement with universitas education reuters

text: 5 minutes ago BRIEF-WSFS Financial Reaches Settlement With Universitas Education Reuters Staff Feb 27 (Reuters) - WSFS Financial Corp: * WSFS REACHES SETTLEMENT WITH UNIVERSITAS EDUCATION, LLC * WSFS FINANCIAL CORP - ‍WSFS SETTLED CASE FOR $12.0 MILLION TO AVOID UNCERTAINTIES OF ARBITRATION AND TO END EXPENSE OF ONGOING LITIGATION​ * WSFS FINANCIAL-‍SETTLEMENT REQUIRES CO TO UPDATE PREVIOUSLY REPORTED Q4 EARNINGS,REDUCING REPORTED AFTER-TAX EARNINGS BY ABOUT $9.3 MILLION,OR $0.29/SHARE Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
